      "text": "私が海で遊びたかったのは\n小さい頃の反動もあるかもしれませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe me wanting so badly to play at the beach\nwas because of my childhood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "実家にいた頃は毎日習い事ばかりで\n友達と海で遊ぶなんて許されなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I lived with my parents‚ I had so many things to study every day.\nThey never allowed me to play with my friends at the beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
