      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "だから今日みたいにみんなで海に来て\nスイカ割りをしたり、ビーチバレーをしたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So everybody going to the beach like today‚\nwith watermelon splitting‚ beach volleyball‚ all that…",
